OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fbecoming largely clear, although late
OL,7,Fin the night low cloud may creep
OL,8,Facross parts of Hampshire, while
OL,9,Fpatchy mist may develop elsewhere. The
OL,10,Fwind easing to a light breeze for most
OL,11,Fplaces.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FDry and largely sunny,
OL,14,Ffeeling warm or very warm, although
OL,15,Fpatchy cloud developing in places. The
OL,16,Flight breeze strengthens during the
OL,17,Fday especially along the south coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
