OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fat times with variable cloud for much
OL,7,Fof the period, staying mostly dry with
OL,8,Fhazy sunshine at times. Temperatures
OL,9,Flikely above average, becoming very
OL,10,Fwarm or hot in places.
